## 5  Manual Actions

```elixir
# Manually trigger a SyntheticDataReactor run
concept = "Erlang distribution and fault tolerance"

Reactor.run(
  HermesBeam.Workflows.SyntheticDataReactor,
  %{concept_to_explore: concept}
)
|> IO.inspect(label: "SyntheticDataReactor")
```

```elixir
# Run a single AgentLoop turn interactively
agent_id = "paste-your-agent-uuid-here"
prompt   = "What do you know about my coding preferences?"
task     = :deep_reflection

Reactor.run(
  HermesBeam.Workflows.AgentLoop,
  %{agent_id: agent_id, user_prompt: prompt, task_type: task}
)
|> IO.inspect(label: "AgentLoop")
```

